OL,3,CSNP urges Burnham to give 'straight
OL,4,Canswers' on Downing Street plans
OL,6,FThe SNP has urged Andy Burnham to give
OL,7,F"straight answers" on what his plans
OL,8,Fare if he takes over as prime minister.
OL,10,FThe former Manchester mayor, who won
OL,11,Fthe Makerfield by-election last week,
OL,12,Fis the leading candidate to take over
OL,13,Ffrom Sir Keir Starmer, who announced
OL,14,Fon Monday he would stand down.
OL,16,FNo other candidate has yet announced
OL,17,Fthey will stand, meaning Mr Burnham
OL,18,Fcould be chosen without a contest if
OL,19,Fhe secures enough support when
OL,20,Fnominations close on July 16.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
