CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782267480
OL,3,CSNP urges Burnham to give 'straight
OL,4,Canswers' on Downing Street plans
OL,6,FBut the SNP's Westminster leader, Dave
OL,7,FDoogan, has pushed for Mr Burnham to
OL,8,Flay out his programme, particularly on
OL,9,Fthe UK's fiscal rules, re-joining the
OL,10,FEU and paving the way for Scotland to
OL,11,Fhold a second independence referendum.
OL,13,F"Andy Burnham and his allies have been
OL,14,Fsuccessful in the choreography of
OL,15,Fremoving a prime minister, but
OL,16,Fchoreography isn't change," Mr Doogan
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782267480
OL,3,CSNP urges Burnham to give 'straight
OL,4,Canswers' on Downing Street plans
OL,6,F"The only thing people really know
OL,7,Ffrom the last few weeks is that Andy
OL,8,FBurnham loves U-turning every bit as
OL,9,Fmuch as Keir Starmer."
OL,11,F"Until now, people have been
OL,12,Fdeliberately left in the dark as to
OL,13,Fwhat Andy Burnham will actually change
OL,14,Fwhen this likely political coronation
OL,15,Ftakes place.
OL,17,F"It is now time that Andy Burnham put
OL,18,Fthat right and actually gave some
OL,19,Fstraight answers on what he intends to
OL,20,Fdeliver as prime minister.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]sD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782267480
OL,3,CSNP urges Burnham to give 'straight
OL,4,Canswers' on Downing Street plans
OL,6,F"Burnham will only pass the test of
OL,7,Fchange if he delivers a bold change of
OL,8,Fdirection from the failure of this UK
OL,9,FLabour Government.
OL,11,F"That means ripping up the
OL,12,Fstraitjacket of the Tory fiscal rules
OL,13,Fwhich Keir Starmer kept, reversing the
OL,14,Fmadness of Brexit and re-joining the
OL,15,FEuropean Union, and finally respecting
OL,16,Fthe democratic rights of countries in
OL,17,Fthe UK to determine their own future.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782267480
OL,3,CSNP urges Burnham to give 'straight
OL,4,Canswers' on Downing Street plans
OL,6,F"Less than two years ago, the Labour
OL,7,FParty promised people change ` two
OL,8,Fyears later they are making exactly
OL,9,Fthe same promise."
OL,11,FMr Burnham's team has been contacted
OL,12,Ffor comment.
OL,14,FSpeaking on BBC Radio Scotland on
OL,15,FTuesday, Scottish Secretary Douglas
OL,16,FAlexander, who has backed Mr Burnham's
OL,17,Fbid for Downing Street, said he would
OL,18,F"set out his thinking if he becomes
OL,19,Fprime minister", but added: "We have
OL,20,Fbeen very clear that we oppose
OL,21,Findependence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]zD@AOU{D@OO]{D@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782267480
OL,3,CSNP urges Burnham to give 'straight
OL,4,Canswers' on Downing Street plans
OL,6,F"We oppose an independence referendum,
OL,7,Fand I think, frankly, the huge
OL,8,Fappetite, not just in Scotland, but
OL,9,Facross the UK, is that we need to
OL,10,Fleave behind decades of constitutional
OL,11,Fdivision and instead focus on
OL,12,Fdelivery."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
